name: Amia Miley (young version)
description:
Amia Miley

She left us too soon...her face, anyway. This is exclusively taken from pre-surgery Amia Miley photographs. You can add in whatever prompts you lie to bring her to present day, but you'd be wrong.

FUN FACT: This is the first textual inversion I've done on a subject that I've actually been with. Take that for what you will.

From a run of 10,000 steps I pulled the 4000 step sample and think it's the most realistic.

Built on v1.5, as per usual she looks best on all of the nicer Models available here.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
